        <Document ID="14FECC50-DC64-40C3-B123-C188931B1BC5">
            <Title>Ramrod Lonnie into rover</Title>
            <Text>With both hands, you hoist Lonnie to a standing position and stare straight into his bloodshot eyes.

“Enough fooling around. Show me these aliens of yours. And then you’re taking me to your grow operation.” Spinning him around, you frogmarch him up into the rover’s cab.

“But Bill,” he pleads. “I need to do some maintenance before I take her out again.” 

Aside from the grime, the rover looks fine. You suspect Iverson knows you’re onto his weed-growing operation and want him to take you to it. Nevertheless, Mars is a harsh mistress. Maintenance isn’t something to be taken lightly.

&gt; Get into the rover with him.
&gt; Go pee and let Lonnie do his maintenance.</Text>
